parameters.name: EvaluationId
parameters.description: The task ID of the evaluation task to which the trace belongs.

parameters.name: Keyword
parameters.description: The keyword to query from the evaluation inputs.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number. Page starts from page 1. Default value: 1

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Maximum value: 50. Default value: 10.
